S There are lots of important things in our life. However, in most cases, they are depends on the priorities we have and acceptation we are awaiting from it. If it fulfill our dreams and aims or not? First of all, let us start with one of the most important things in our life and that is the health. Our mind and body will be so much satisied as we give our body at least the minimum of our time. What I am trying to say is that a certain form of a physical activity per week is beneficial in many facets of our life. That is to say, If you lead an active life, your body appreciate it when you get older. On the other side, those who prefer not to have an active life and their afforts to put their time in anactivity have a bad perspective when they get older. Moreover, their lifestyle is probably aimed to work and earning money. All things considered, it seems reasonable to revise our free time ana to think it over, if we have what we wanted.
