S When we are talking about travel, we have to reduce our thinking only on avaliable method of transportation. There are variety of transport systems available at the moment. For instance, we can travel on railway, on the road, in the air and the last one posible choice is under the ground. That is sounds good. We can travel anywhere and anytime we want. However, if we are want to be somewhere at specific time and something has happened on our journey, what would we do? Well, the solution is in the science and the future. As I has read in the last six months, most of the companies have been trying to bring a solution to get somewere more faster then now. Any researchers brought fast trains and another fast cars. what is more, there is also a car that provides its passangers to get to theairport faster then by taxi. That is a car use a similar system as planes do, but for short distances. Maybe it is a future for transport system in big towns. It does not produce any emissions lake carbon or sound. As far as I am concerned, I gess that the future of transportation, let say travelling in the air is an issue number one. Finally, it seems reasonable to act for supporting of the science. There is no choice for the future, if we do not want to destroy our environment completely.
