S My reason for learning English Everybody who try to learn a forein language know that it is not an easy thing to do, but we continously trying to improve it and progress because of our private reasons which keep us motivated. What are your reasons for keeping doing it? I have been learning english for 15 years and during this time my reason kept chainging. First time when I started to learn english was in primary school when I was teenager. The reason that I seek for new knowledge was that I had to do it. I did not care too much about English language itself, I was forced to comprahend basic stuff to graduate to another year. At the moment I regret that I did not pay more attention to it, I am certainly sure that i would help me in my future. Once, I heard a great quote which basically says that the smartest people learn from other's people mistakes. So I really recommend to learn form my mistake and respect your time by not wasting it.
