S My reasons for learning English are these ones. In the first place, English is a passion, in fact, a lot of people like English because at first, it was created for being the simplest language in the world in contrast with French language that was the loy language for its complexity. Then, English language is really appreciate to be pronounced because it's sweet and melodic ! In the second place, English is an avantage in the professional and social world ! As a matter of fact, a lot of country talks English like Australia, United States of America, England... And for study in these countries, you had to pass English exam like TOEFL or IELTS. Moreover, when two people coming from two different countries are meeting, they usually talk English to undersand each other. As a conclusion, you can travel around the world with learning English.
