S Many of us complain about health when we get older. We do not have had enough time to take care of ourselves. There are lots of reasons for what we assumed different life standards of being. On one hand, some of us changed their priorities. What is more, instead they take care of their hallth, theycare of their money income. On the other hand, those who started their active life when they were young, their habbits survived till their adulthood. They fully understood that the more beneficial for life is to keep your exercise routine at lest two times per week in a roundabout kind of way. Money took their second place in their personal life. As far as I am concerned, I would say that my personal experience is to stay in shape or to be healthy than to have a lot of money. If I have a power to change something in todays rush time, I would set out three day off work, or shorten the workhours in order people have more time for their families.
