S Learning is one of the fundamental processes that helps you to keep your mind in a good condition. For example, you make connection among cells of your brain and make your memory stronger. However, people are trying to increase their ability to memorize information by variety of different ways. On one hand, a competition is a basic way how to persuade schoolchildren to care about their mental health and develop ability of picking up information from variety of sources. On the other hand, the midlle-aged people prefer to learn through reading and practicing. An appropriate way of education is work in groups and communication which seems to be the most important. Adults as me found out that learning English as a second language offers both. Communication is important when you are trying to find a well-ppaid job, or want to travel. Secondly, learning language grings you a new level of positive thinking and expanding your memory needed when you get older.
