S The school of the future! The world and technology develop is such a quick pace. The current education system is quite different than our grandparents remember. In what ways do you think schools will be different in the future? I believe that learning in calss where is other 30 people is not effective, thus to increase the quality of learing the amount of student in the calss might be decreased to about 10 people. The other way to improve it is to create appropriate books or online talk so students could learn from home. In the future textbooks will be replaced by personal computers, so you will not have to carry very heavy backpack. The scientists might also find a better system, how to comprehend the knowledge quicker. So, it will reduce years which we spend in school. That is a difficult question to answer, beacause the future is unpredictible. Howewer, I am sure that the education will be different and more efficient than it is now.
