S A report about what i want to achieve in new school year Introductions: The aim of this report is to present the information about what I want to achieve in new school year to my English teacher. The areas of learning I am pleased: I believe that both listening and reading skills are very strong. Exams from previous year confirmed this infomration, so I can spend a bit less time on learing these areas. The ares of learning I want to improve: There are many areas I want to improve, but the writting skill is my biggest weakness. Spelling is the area where I make the most mistakes. Second area is gramma, which is quite complex topic so I will have to spend a lot of time to improve it to satisfactory level. Conclusion: It seems that, overall, I have some strong areas like listening and reading and I have to put more efforn on improving writting. I am going to practise much more than before what hopefully will benefit in the future. Karol Roldi College student
