S Every every student is different. So every students needs different education to be proper for him. It may be called "tailar made education." But it is very costful to provide tailar made education to each student in the present system. Actually thirty or more students are gathered in one classroom. And they are taught at the average level education. The advanced student are bored. At same time, there are student who can't catch up with the lessons. There a few students who are satisfied in the classroom. It seems that IT and AI will solve this problem in the future. The AI evaluates the capability of each student. The computer shows the content which fits for each student. Every students seems to studying at their level. If there wasn't group eduation, parents would worry that their children lost the oppourtunities to learn human relationship. Of course I don't think the physical education class with one student. The group education will remain. But the tailor made eduation will be prevaing the future, too.
