S Tevevision gives us a variety of contents, news, drama, music, talk show, education, religion, and shopping. I don't watch tv as much as before. All tv programs are just one-way. Whatever I want, it force information to me from the start to the end. Although sometimes tv entertains me, it often frastrates me. I don't like to watch TV anymore. Recently we can choose favorite programs to entertain us on the netflix. It is not necessary to turn the tv on. TV has been educating us in Japan. When I was a child, we watched a tv program on the education channnel. The contents were "be nice to the elder," "don't behave egoistically in public." In this sense tv can educates but is really one-way. The one-way class gives us a lot of information and knowledge but doesn't give us a opportunity to learn deeply.
