S I live in the Czech republic where you can find at least four zoos. Moreover, each of the zoo has offers their visitors a certain kind of entertainment as well. People in our country usually comes to the zoos to see the animals and the majority of them want to escape from busy daily life. However, a certain persentage of people comes to educate their children and among them are schools that organizing educational programes. Nedless to say, we do not see the animals in the zoos as the prisoners, we see them as a thing that has roots in our mind as an entartainment. On the other side, I have never thought about it in the way that those animals belong to the nature as well as human. Imagine that you will take a place of animals in the zoo tommorow. It seems as a terrible imagination, isn't it? What I am trying to say is that we do not turn a blind eyes on animals and make the most for their better future.
