S My favourite season of the year is the spring. The spring season gives you an anergy you need after a long winter. It fills you up with energy. To obtain an energy from the sun, I usually spend my free time in the garden which is a good advice for many people who want to do something useful and simultaneously take off from tidy daily routines \u2013 in a roundabout kind of way. Not to mention your immune system which needs to fill up the battery as well to work properly. Secondly, the spring brings you an opportunity to set off somewhere to look around or visit castle. My best choise is to assume this season as a start to achieve your new goals such as reduce your weight or become better in some sport activity. If you have the possibility like me and you live near the national park, you would try cycling or walking. As far as I am concerned, movement in the fresh air is the best start to a new season.
