S This is it! It is here! Look through the window. Spring is comming! My very favourite season of the year. I want to say, I like all the season of the year, but when the first flowers came out and the grass is getting a little bit more greener as it was for to or three days ago. The sun is shinning a little bit more brighter and the wind is whispering that the snow has gone and he has the smell of easiness. The most of the people you will meet, you will see a smile on their face and maybe you notice the same easiness at the people as you felt when the wind was whispering in your ears and stroke across your skin. In this time I will only take my camera, go out very day long and take a picture of all the new life I will found outside. This makes the spring so special for my. It is bringing new life to the earth, every year and I want the easiness I feel through the spring, it will be with me the whole year.
