S Volunteer work is a way for students to help an association for disabled people, or a community for exemple gays left in the street by their parents, or Black and Latinos people who are victims of racism... For integrate an university, students usually have to do volutneering. In the first place I'll tell why it's really good for them but in the second place I'll tell why I think it have convenients. In the first place, makes volunteering an obligation force students to help other people and see what is going on for people in need of help. It can makes them consciensious about poverty, violence, sickness and develop their compassion. In the second place, I think it havn't to be necessary. In fact, it seems good at first sight but in effect some students do that only for university and when they are in the association, they help nobody or are unpleasant. The best way to correct this error is this one: universitys should add a reccomendation letter in the folder of the student, then the association or the person concern of the student's volunteering can explain the behavior of this one. With that, even if student don't like volunteering, he's obliged to do his work well.
