S Write and improve is a good platform to practice your writing in your free time because many time we spend a lot time in other things and we neglect contanct with the English language. This medium is very easy to use, you just need internet and create account, in the platform are any topic with different level. I really like this platform because I can practice at any time with my computer or my cell phone from my home or work. In my experience I have been improved very fast, every day I write one or two report and that is very satisfactory to me. I think that is a good idea that the teachers will recommend this platform to his students. this is a great working tool that should be using by all people that want learn English. At this moment I have an intermediate level.
