S I think Writing and Improve is a really good website. It makes me improve my English writing. In this website, there is a timer so I know what time I need to write. There are a level and a test zone, so I can prepare for my exam. It gives information from the first writing until the last writing so I knpw my progress. People doesn't need to use their money because the website is free and people can donate their money to this website if they get satisfy. But, I sometimes a little bit scare because this website ask my biodata or my family life, even thought there are something that normal to ask. I feel that this website asking something over and over, I don't know It will be the negative things or not. But, I think this is still worth It. I don't feel deficiency from this website, so I will recommend my classmates to try Write and Improve.
