S Come to London and enjoy our parks, pubs, museums and stores! London has the most famous clock around the world. The Big Bang is open daily from 7 a.m. until 11 p.m. You can visit it, but you had to pay for getting in it. Also, you can shop everything you want on the street Very Cheap. It is very close to most of the accommodations in the city. You don't need to take a taxi. Please if you want to visit some parks, pay attention and use the wastebasket to dispose of your waste. If you put it on the floor, you will receive a fine. At night the stars shine, so do the pubs. You can find many different bars around the city.
