S In my view every child should play the proper video game for his age. You can't give to a child an 18+ game. Also, I think that such video games like shooting or fighting is not apropriate for children at any age. I know cases where the child grown to be a violent person and that put him even in prison. I really think that a child shoud play video games which will help him to evolve and become a better persone. As a second view too much video games affects anyone. After a long perios you wouldn't be able to see straight and your health will be also affected. I would end with my strongly opinion that in childhood every parent must educate his child to spend more time socializing in real life, to play, to evolve and to study, not to play video games all day in the house.
