S I am very surprised with your letter. A birthday celebrating in you country seems to be a bit boring. In our country people usually celebrate their birthday many way. We are the nation of improvisations. To give an illustration, I celebrated my last birthday at the campsite. Others decided to run a marathon or to rich a peak of a mountain. By and large, your celebration depends on your expectation and ideas you would like to experience. Do not forget, you are the only person to say how to celebrate your birthday.
