S I started to practice writing three months ago to prepare for the IELTS exam the next summer and until now I still a beginner where I wrote fifty paragraphs in that stage and I plan to arrive at one hundred paragraphs before the exam date. After that, I started by writing with the website Write and Improve in order to choose topics and Grammarly App for proofreading, also I will watch some videos on Youtube about methods of developing writing skill and technics writing for the IELTS exam Honestly, I liked this experience as a practice, and I was not expecting it beautiful and enjoyable where I had little fear to learn it but I still in the beginning. Writing skills is very important for learning any language specifically for whoever wants to continue studying and for sure I recommend learning it.
