S I would like to write a report about Write and Improve. After my English teacher recommended it, I has practiced writing skill by using it. I like this system. Firstly, I can try a lot of tasks to improve writing skill. After making a sentence, I can check my mistakes by sending it to Write and Improve. My wrong points are highlighted, so I know what I should have a mistake in my sentence and I can correct my answer. I like the fact that I can study by myself. Secondly, the correction of my sentence is done immediately by AI algorythm. It is useful system for me. Thirdly, the cost is free though there are a lot of contents which is available. In the meanwhile, I dont like in one point. the correction is sometimes made a mistake. I hope this program is better than now. In summary, I usually use Write and Improve. I think it's a useful application. I will recommend my friends to use it strongly.
