S I am a teacher and I had lived that matter in my study as a student or in my career as a teacher so I prefer the different teachers for the student for several reasons: First: as a student you have must know and learn of the different methods to studying and build learn skills from more than one teacher where every teacher have a special way of teaching then that experience make your learning more flexible and able to more learning whatever the difficulties. Second: even with a weak teacher you will be able to self-learning specifically within the Internet which is brought up a major revolution in the self-learning field an I always say to my students they can replace any teacher in their school with the Internet where there is a countless website to learn any material you want whether on Youtube or any learning platform in various fields. Third: the learn from just one teacher may make the student a negative student and limits his ability to learn from various sources. Finally: Perhaps in primary school the children's students need one teacher in order to the strong establish in learning reading and writing basics.
