S Write and Improve represents a great way to update your English skills. It helps even you vocabulary. The best thing to do is to have a daily schedule to follow. You can write at least 30 rows a day. One of the best thing is to write a lot becuase when you are writing, you are studyying how to express yourself and you are searching for new words and phrases. Write and Improve has his good points but it also has his weaknesses. You can spend to much time on the writing part and neglect the speaking, listening or grammar parts. With writing you cand improve a lot you English but if you exagerate, you cand spend to much on it and damage the other parts of English. Writing is important but don't forget about speaking, listening, reading and the grammar parts.
