S From my view the same teacher is good when you are in elementary school because you need a teacher and a role model. You need that teacher for at least 4 years. The teacher have to know you and your parents and why not even your hobbies. He must teach you how to become responsible and how to take life in your own hands. A different teacher also helps you a lot, because you get to know diferent views of life and different personalities. From every human being you can learn something good or bad. You can make a selection of your learning from all your teachers. To summarise if you have the same teacher you can have a good role model and a good second parent but if you will have many different teachers, you will learn what diversity means and a lot of new visiona about life .
