S In 2006 launched the government of Saudi the king Abdullah program for the scholarship to study bachelor and master and doctorate, so that program make a lot of students in Saudi front golden chance to abroad for the study where the conditions were very easy to study in the United state or United kingdom or some countries. This program was a qualitative leap to education progress in Saudi and now there are thousands of graduates came back after end their studying, so I see it as a great advantage for any student if he can study abroad specifically in scientific sections and economy or management. The advantages of studying abroad are many like learning a new language and identify new cultures and communities and increase self-confidence and independence. Concerning disadvantages perhaps some students suffer their distance from the family, therefore, feel to depression and isolation leading to affect negatively on their studying.
