S What I learned: I am happy I learn in the last school year about some things. First: reading four English books. Second: I listened for more than four hundred hours to English podcasts on my phone. Third: I finished studying a diploma of sciences of psychology and social online by Namaa Acadamy center website. What I would like to improve in my learning: First: I need to improve in four skills of English: speaking, writing, reading, and listening. Second: I need to study some methods of education in physics teaching for high school students and implement what I see suitable. What I want to achieve to learn: I would like to get a good degree in the IELTS examination the next summer and that is the main target in new school year. Perhaps after finish the IELTS exam I will study some courses online by Coursera online or any website educational.
