S In one way television is a good thing. With television we can educate children and even grown ups. For children we can have some educational shows like maths, chemestry or even phisics. We can concentrate even on climate change and try to educate people from a young age to be responsible and to recycle. The most important televizion shows must be on education. In another way we must have some entertaining in television like comedy, drama, horror or action. Television is about entertaining people, we must show to all the world that it's worth it to watch TV and if we are good in comercial we can even convice them that it's a must. To sum all of this I must add the fact that health is also important and we must exercise, so 24 hour of TV won't help us in this matter.
