S For English learners, finding useful tools is important thing to improve their English skills. Actually, I used a lot of tools before now. I sometimes gave some of them up immediately and some of them are not fit for me in the view of improving my English skills. Recently, my friends recommended a tool named Write and Improve and I tried to use it. As a result, I was impressed because the tool is one of the best tools for me. Accordingly, I want to write a revies about it. Write and Improve is a sentence correction tools by AI algorithm method. There are a lot of tasks in it. We choose a task among them and make a sentence. When we sent it to Write and Improve, AI checks our sentence and score it. It also highlights wrong sentences and suggest what to correct. There are several levels in it and it can be used various English learners. It is definitely a useful tool, but it is not a perfect one. For example, we can get feedback after correcting our answer, but we can't know wrong parts exactly. Additionally, our score is defined in each levels even if the answer is excellent. I hope these two point would be improved. In summary, I write a review about Write and Improve. It's an excellent and useful tool for English learners. I hope many people use this tool and it will be improved continueously.
