S Hi Jeff, How have you been? I went to a concert last week. The artist was Misia whom you also like. My friend called me two weeks ago and he asked me if I would go to the concert. He would go with his friend, but his friend would have an important appointment and he couldn't go there. Of course, I accepted his proposal and I was excited. While I looked at Misia's performance, I couldn't supress my emotion and I was standing during the concert. As I expected, her singing is excellent and it was the first experience for me to cry with no reason by her song. I reccomend her concert. If you have any chance, please look at her performance and move it like me. Regards, Akihiro
