S Learning second language is become more popular after Internet because the world become a small town and people needs to comunicate with each others so they learn their languages, and English is the most popular language in these days because a lot of reasons but that is not what I want to talking about now. How I learned English ? Let me tell you secret that is evrey one know it , I learned English with myself from the Internet for the last 6 months ago I wake up evrey day and decide to learn something new and some words after that I focused on grammer and how to connect words to make sentences. To be honest the most helpful things that is help me and makes me learn fast is Write&Improve website because I am alone and I need to practice writing and I try to find some website which use AI in the process of learning and I found this great website. If you ask how Write&Improve website work ? They are give you some taskes and tell you write about these taskes so, you can choose your level. I write in the advance level now and it's really helpful. I think you want to learn English if you arrived to this point and as gift let me give you some recommendation and resources to learn English you should try Youtube , Write&Improve , learn new words solve some problem and stay motivated.
