S Hello teacher, As today we had a class discussion about healthy life, I realize that doing exercise is necessary to have a healthy life, but even at that point, there are more important things than healthy life, like family, friends and more... But, without a healthy life you couldn't live that much to appreciate those points that I wrote before. So what I'm thinking is... Healthy live is pretty good, but even in the good moments of that life, it could let you fall and may make you start again from all way up. As you probably know, there are very addicting things, like biscuits or other kind of sweets that could make you loose you healthy life work progress that aren't that bad, but I just really think that having stops for eating some sweets aren't bad, I mean, if you have a healthy life and you think that you'll like some sweets but you are scared about falling down that effort, don't worry, just eat them in a very small quantities.... Get rekt teacher.
