S I'm writing to inform about a university life. When we disicuss about the school life, it's difficult to answer below the question. Which is better to choose an university, which is located in your own living place or not? I think there are srong point and weak point each other. Firstly, I explain about when students live in remote location to go to university. By living there, they have to do various kinds of tasks by themselves. As a result, they will change their mind and they can prepare to become full-fledged members of society. On the other hand, their parents have to have a certain burden more money. Secondly, I'd like to have an opinion about when students stay at home. they have more free time than the students who iive in remote place, because their parents support dairy houseworks. Moreover, there is no need about extra living fee by staying with their own family. Therefore, they don't need to work hard to suport family budget. As a result, they can have more experiences for them. they will affect their future life. When I went to university, I lived in remote place. I could change my mind by doing by myself. Both have a strong point and a weak point, but I recommend former one in the view of my experience.
