S Health is life\u00B4s fuel, in other words, health is what keeps you alive. So, the trick is finding a way to be healthier. That said, one of the most popular paths to reach healthiness is through exercise. But, most people forget that the exercise needs to come along with a healthy food as well. Furthermore, there is another thing which is forgotten and it plays an important rule on our life: our mind. So, even though the exercise is important to make our bodies stronger, the exercise itself is not enough. If your mind is not healthy, it won\u00B4t be able to stablish a good connection with your body and so the exercise won\u00B4t provide you all the benefits that it has. Therefore, the most important thing in life, in my point of view, is being able to build up a healthy mind and body. If you are able to keep it, you will have time and strenght to chase other things like success, happiness and goals.
