S I know that I\u00B4m always trying to show a different version of myself to people, especially to those who I apreciate the most. I put a mask and an armor intending to be as frigid and cold-hearted as someone could be. But on the inside I\u00B4m a romantic and passionate woman even though I try to hide it even from me. What I\u00B4m trying to say is that one of my favourites films is a romantic one called: "Will you marry me?." It\u00B4s filled with passion,love and comedy. It\u00B4s about a woman who is travelling to ask to his fianc\u00E9 in marriage because of a cultural tradition. On her way to meet him, she find a charming man to help her and they experience hilarious and unique moments. Will her feel in love to this strange man or her love to her fianc\u00E9 will be stronger than this?
