S How'dy,Neighbor! Well,If you don't mind,can you look after my house while we're on vacation? These are a few thing that you must pay attetion into it. First,house keys. We gave you the house key and you must keep it in a safe place that others won't see easily,watch out for thiefs too. Second,plants. We have two peony in the house,so you have to open the air conditioner at most of the time because it turned out to be in the greenhouse in the past apprently. And the last but not least,pets. We have a cat in the house too,it's called Mi Mi,because it have a so-big appetite,so you have to feed it once in a while. And watch out for other cats coming to our house too. That's it. Your Neighbor, Nikkl
