S Well,l think that l will like the "dark and quiet room" kind pretty good. But it mostly counts on how sleepy you are and how's your sleeping place (all known as sleeping bags and beds) is. lf you are very sleepy and your sleeping place is very noisy,you will still fall fast asleep. But if you are not sleepy and someone make you sleep,no matter how dark and quiet your sleeping place is,you will still be hard to fall asleep. lf you have trouble falling sleep every night,try this method:Take out two dimes,when you go to sleep,place the two dimes on your eye lap,the dime can help you fall asleep. But it have some major problems too. Like you can't use this method when you're sleeping sideways. So l don't really recommend you to do it. lf you really need it,you can only sleep with your face facing up at the ceiling.
