S In order to understand about life, human have created different methods to keep and study several organisms from culture plates to zoos. Zoos are not only to help to understand how several animals behave but to help to keep in safe animals in danger by hunting or because their habitats have been destroyed, besides in many of zoos, environmental conditions are so close similiar to wild environment stimulating animals to reproduce and keeping the breed away from danger to reach the adequate age to putting them in willd habitats. At the same time, zoos have been a good way to show to people, the woth and importance of nature and they have brought all ecosistems and wild life in a little space and to have allow being close and aware to different life forms . However, many zoos do not have space and resources enough to offer a good life to all animals. Some animals have shown behaveorial disorders by locking, like elephants and gorilas. So, I think humanity should get strive to preserve natural spaces where animales live and trying to make people aware about natural conservation and it impact on their lives.
