S Good Day! l already heard what happened to you last week,and what l want to to tell you is that l feel sorry for you. l know how you feel because l have that same experience too. l've been send to a hospital and did a little operation on me. The thing is you are not alone. You still have your friends and family (including me),you can text or talk to them about your feelings,just like we're doing now. Now l sent a box of candy plus a bonquet of flowers to your home. When can l visit you? We can play board games and can still can have fun together. l hope you get better fast! Yours Truely, Alice
