S There are many resources in internet to improve your English learning process, one of them is this: Write and Improve. This resource has been so much useful to me because it has allowed me practising my writing in English and let me know if I use grammar correctly. Besides, Write and Improve help me to built my ideas and find the best way to explain them to others in formal and informal way. The web platform offers several activities in different levels of dificulty. So, you can only describe a photo or write an email or write reports about specfific subjects of academy or business. Thus, my experience using this platform has been fruitful, I have improved my english so much and I have spotted my mistakes and learnt of them because excellent feedback that platform offers. Hence, I recomend a lot this internet resource to improve you English.
