S It was about 10 years ago. I was a teenager going through an important period of self-knowledge and acceptance of my flaws. I was starting to feeling more like a woman than like a child, but I was so insecure about my physical atributes. I didn\u00B4t feel beautiful mostly because of my skin and my lean body. I thought that I didn\u00B4t drew attention of the good looking guys and I was too bashful to make the first move. During that time, me and my family went on a vacation to a breathtaking hotel. Right there I felt so connected with the nature and I must say that with myself as well. I caught the interest of three gorgeous guys and although I didn\u00B4t have anything with them, not even a kiss, it was realy important for my self-esteem. I got out of there a new girl ready to embrace my new version or just my old one.
