S My favourite season of the year is summer. I think it is the best because the weather is nice and you can go to the beach and swimming. I can go swim with my freinds and even my family. In the summer I like to drink a very cold cola. I like to eat icecream. I like the summer because i do not have to wear winter clothes and i fell comfortable with out it. The best reason for why Ilike summer is that we do not have school. For me and other people summer is like a brake from studying and I can rest and be ready for the next year. In the summer it is always holiday. That means that i can travle a lot to other countries and have fun there. I am longing for the summer and I hope it comes as sonn as possible.
