S l think that it's good for students that they have the same teachers and classmates every year,espeically when you're at the high grades. Now let me say why at the down side of this....... l found out that when you have a new teacher in your class,his or her's teaching method is diffrent from your old teacher. This will cause the student to be puzzled because he or she don't know to stand at which side,and eventually this student will have a bad grade in the end of the the trimester compared to the last trimester which is in the last grade. Now a days,people (including parents) will think that we will have more to learn when we have a new teacher every trimester. But that's actually just wrong,when they look at the grades,they will think twice about the new teacher thing. But when they caught on the next trimester,they will think that having a new teacher was still best. It just goes on and on and on. But at last,l still think that having a same teacher was the best.
