S I have been suggested by my teacher to start and use Write and Improve in order to broad my written English skills. My teacher then asked me to report my impressions about this web site including pro and con. I have accepted the suggestion with pleasure as I was actually looking for a web site that could really assist me with the corrections of my written essays, even if, at the beggining, I was expecting to interact directly with someone real so that I could discuss and eventually ask for suggestions in real time. With much suprise, I realised that the way Write and Improve is arranged does not involve a direct human interaction however I can confirm that it is absolutely effective and very helpful. Mosty because it is always available time and you do not need to require any appointment. The suggestions are very helpful and very clear. I will certainy recommend Write and Improve to my classmates if they definitely want to improve their written English at their own speed and for free.
