S I really don\u00B4t mind sleeping in a dark room or in an enlightened place. I sleep like a log, so I won\u00B4t be easily disturbed by any noise. But, I do have some conditions to persue if I want to awake in a good mood. I do need to sleep with a pillow between my legs and also need one extra pillow to embrace, otherwise I am going to wake up with backache. Furthermore, I have to lay down on my side to keep me away from that pain too.
