S Nowadays the technology develops very fast and human finds many new ways to travel. In my opinion travel in the future will have some defferent aspects, but the basic travel will be the same as now. Nowadays you can easily find a video talks about a place, where you want to go. human is developing new real-virtual devices as the glasses which you can see somewhere when you put it on. And you can go to see somewhere but you just sit in the same place. Three D player can give you the view like looking at the real sceen. Some people like aventure would take the new ways to travel. But the rest will choose the basic travel because you can touch, smell, look, see and feel everything around you. You do not have the feeling of air or cool weather when you travel by three D player. The organzise to travel will have some defferent point such as people do not have to go to travel agency to register. People want to go somewhere can inter the internet find the information of tours and register to travel very easy.
