S Everyone wants to be healthy anh wealthy. If you have both of them is very good. if you are rich you can buy anything you want. You can spend your money without considering so much. If you are not rich you would find it is difficult to satisfy your demands. Someone has to choose one of two things health or wealth. I think it is more important to be healthy than to be rich. Because if you are heathy you can do anything. You can study anything you want, and you can help other people also. If you are ill or not healthy you think about only one thing is that how to get health and you can not do anything else. If a man was ill for long time, he would want to be died. Some people do anything to be rich without considering their health and then they would spend all their money to buy medicines for keeping their health.
