S From my view, I would love if I could study at some musical instrument in high school. It's a difficult thing to aproach because you need student if you want to mantain this type of subject in school but you also cannot force students from informatics specialization to do it. A solution could be to implement a different type of stuying class. A teacher could be paid to have some classes during the week and every student from every class or grade could attend. In this way we can satisfy the lack of students and the teacher could teach with entuziasm. I think that students could develop great skills by learning to sing at an instrument. I saw a lot of people who developted a good thinking by learning to sing at some instrument. They where literally learning more easier everything at school. In the end I would like to highlight that not all school are willing to develop singing classes.
