S Hey are booth good choises. It depends on each case because if you family has a lot of money than it is better for the student to stay somwere alone. He could study better and could improve his experience in life. On the other way if the student stays with his family because they don't have money to pay his rent,it can be difficult to keep in touch with his classmates but he will be near his family and it could be easier form him in though times. Every situation comes with it's good parts and bad parts and it depends on the family's buged or on the family's perception. To put it in another way, the family could have the needed money but they think that their child could learn better under their eyes so he could be overseen or they literally don't want to waste the money on a rent.
