S In my opinion, the books in schools and universities should be replaced completely by tabletes and computers because of some reasons as bellow: First, the computers and tablets can store a huge number of books. One tablets can store as many books as a bid library does. Second, students can find the books in tablets faster 100 times than finding the books in libraries. Students can find the books in other libraries in one sencond without going to that libraries. Third, students can write, draw or anything else on only one tablet. When they do something wrong, they can fix it easily by retyping or erase the wrong things. Fouth, Students do not have to bring so many books to school or unversity, it is convinient for them. Fifth, each country does not have to print so many books for students, it means that we can reduce the materials for making books. It will reduce the bad effects to environment.
