S I incidentally find out a website, which helps me to write and improve my English writing skils. That is writeandimprove. com website. It provides you many useful feature for writing English easay. It is devided to three levels suitable to your English level. You can choose your level as beginner, intermediate or advanced. There are many topics in each section, you can choose the topics you want. It allow you to set the time for writing to know that how long you writng an easay, and you can reset the timer at any time you want. After writing an easay you can click the button "Check," for a while the program will show your mistakes on the monitor and recommend the replacements, it also evaluate the level of your easay. At first program shows and highlights you the first mistake and suggest the replacement. When you click the "Next" button it will move to the next mistake. By that way you can review and check whole of your easay. After that you can come back your easay to fix the mistakes in the easay. After fixing all mistake you can click the button "Check" again to check your easy, and program reevaluate you easay. You would know how your easay is improved. It also changes the colour of some sentances but I do not understand. I think It would be better if there is a guidance for that.
