S My English teacher has kindly required us to produce a plan for the forthcoming new school year where we are going to highlight the subjects we love the most, the area we need to improve and the actions we envision to take to achieve our objectives. I would start by saying that I have always loved studing history and philosophy for they both represent the physical and psychological path of humanity . Being so passionate about them, I would like attend a seminar about the medieval age arranged by the local Museum of Medieval History while for phylosophy I am planning to attend an on-line course so that I will be able to deepen my studies. On the other hand, I definitely need to improve my knowledge about mathematics and geometry mainly considering that these two subjects will be part of the scholar trail for the next four years. To reach a good level, I have decided to purchase private classes in addition to those already foreseen at school. In conclusion, I hope to have identified the right ways to meet the objectives highlighted above in order to render this new school year as much effective for myself as possible.
