S once upon the time human knew to sing. At that time human did not have music intruments as nowadays but remember the melody of the song and then human invented the music intruments to simulate the tone of voice. I my opinion, studying music should be required in all schools because of some reasons as bellow: First, every one needs to develop both physicque and mental. To develop physicque, human need to do activities such as running, walking, climbing, working, etc. but to develop mental human need to study including studying music. Second, studying music will help one understand the msic notes. Music notes simulate different tone of voice and devided into 14 defferent frequency. Each person can rewrite his tone by himseft and he can compose his owner song. Third, studying music will help developing human's brain completely. It will help to study the social subjects such as literature, history, psychology, geography,etc. Fourth, studying music and singing will help strengthen throat mucles and the result is making human's voice clearer.
