S I like to choose moving away and living on my own while I am attending university because of some reasons: Firstly, I am I am readly an adult man when I am a students in university, and I understand what is right to do. According to our country laws, I have the right to do every thing on my own right ways. Secondly, I will become more confident when I live alone because I have to think what i should do, how to do and I have to decide every thing. I cannot make a call phone to my mother to ask how to do some thing. I have the full responsibility for every my action. All that things make me more confident. Thirdly, I have to contrive to live on money I earn every month. I am forced to think, to find the way for living because I am in difficult situation. That things urge me more active and dynamic. Fourthly, I make as many friends as I can. I am not forbited to meet or make friend someone.
