S I do not know that learning to foreign languages is important these days. In my mind it depends on the situation. If you have no ambitions and you are a lazy person, this is not for you. But if you are curious about the world, learning to foreign languages is very important. Especially if your mother language speaks only to people in your country and if you want to travel or have really nice and well paid work. Speaking some foreign language gives you the opportunity to travel and live wherever you want. You can meet a lot of people, change the experiences, make new friends and maybe find the love of your life. Learning other languages opens your mind for new experiences. When do you learn new languages you get to know new culture, the culture of people who speaks this language. In Summary, I can say that speaking more than languages is very important to have a better and more interesting life. Especially for me.
