S Acorrding to my imagantion,l think that in the future,we will have some kind of device to transport ourselfs to anywhere. You just press a button or tell the device where you want to go,then you will be right to your destanation. But that probably won't be nessecary until the next 2400 had came. So now,let's just talk about the late 2100s. You can read the next paragraph to get more imformation. First,cars. The cars right now isn't a big hit for human civilization. But in the future? Then it will be a whole different story. In fact,l can bet you 500 dollars that in the future,the cars will be armed with radar GPS,TV,and a snack bar just in case that the passenger or driver is a bit hungry. The cars can be molded to be any shape,just like Transformers. And most of all,the engine can be on full power (which is 350 miles an hour) to 6-12 hours. Plus,there will be high tech weapons in case of a attack,and it can be compeletly camaflaged to the things that is around the car.
