S Nowadays there are many problems in the rural areas, because most of people are moving to the cities, and they are leaving the field which give us our food. Because of that there is a lack of doctors in small villages, and this could be very dangerous, if an elderly don't receive medical care in the right time, he or she could die early. First of all, we need doctors everywhere but many doctor don't want to be posted to small villages or towns. This is a problem and the reasons for this problem are uncountables. One main reason could be the less money that the doctors earn when they are working in rural areas, because they working less hours and their works are more bored, besides if they are young they won't have many things to do and enjoy in this kind of villages, although a doctor in a small town or village has a very quite and calm life besides the charm of living in the field. Second, the solutions for these problems are very easy and very hard at the same time, because the main solution could be that the elderly move to big cities (however this is not gonna happen, like all of us know), another solution could be improve the work conditions of the doctors which work in small villages or give them prizes in order to boost their willing to be posted to this areas. In conclusion we have to take care of our rural areas and elderly people beside of take care of ourselves and like it is said in my village "an apple a day keeps the doctor away," this is my today's piece of advise.
