S It is well known that day after day the requirements in the studies are now more difficult than before and some high schools are asking for volunteer work in order to graduate. there is a lot of controversia about this fact in our society, because some people think that teenagers are too young to do this kind of work while the other part has the opposite point of view. On the one hand, we have to say that hard work could teach and boost skills in the teenagers besides the fact that when they are doing this kind of activity they are far from dangerous zones, gangs and other harm stuff, for instance in Spain there are some programs to teach about farming and these programs are done in army bases around the country. The volunteer work that is made by teenagers could provide them with true knowledge which they could use in their real lives, for example when you work preparing food for poor people, this work gives you two benefits, one the kitchen lessons and the other could be a different perspective of our society. On the other hand, we have to be carefull about the situations that our teenagers are exposed, for instance if they are not under super the supervision of an adult they could harmful relations with the people that should receive the volunteer work, for example if they are working some drug dealer could offer them drugs. To sum up with both points of view in count, I strongly believe that the volunteer work produces a benefit to our society but it has to be done with adults and without stress the student.
