S Books and tehnology The computers and tablets should completely replace books in schools and universities because the books that we are carrying are too heavy and our backs hurts after a day of carrying seven kilos of books. If we would have tablets or laptops, it will be more easier to study and our backs won't hurt, and if we broke or water the books, we need to buy new ones, but, if we have tablets or laptops, we won't break them because they are expensive and we like them. In twenty years, we won't have books, we will have tablets and laptops but why should we have them in tweenty years and not now? That is the big question. My opinion is to replace them now because studying will be more funny because we can wacth videos about that things that we have for school. The tehnology is the future.
