S Hey Jack! I hope everything's OK. I'm so glad to hear that you're coming to my country. First of all, I suggest you go to the Chapultepec castle, you will learn lots of interesting things about my country's history and you're going to fell in love with the unique arquitecture of the place and the breathtaking views. Also you can't miss the new Antropology museum that just opened a month ago, it will be the icing on your cake. By the way, both places are free on Sundays. As for the transportation, you should definitely hire bikes as they're cheaper and more comfortable than public transport and good for doing excersice. Many thanks for invitating me, count me in! Just let me where are we going to meet. Well, I think that's about it. Say hello to everyone. See you soon, C
