S I would like a long, calm life until 100 years in order to enjoy of my life. This is very important to take your time to discover whole the good things on it. There is one expression: take your time, step by step. As the proverb, the rabbit and the turtle from Moliere. You can do everything as much as a person who do the things intensely less faster for sure but you will get the opportunity to do all the things much deeper and with conscious of the things surroundings. That's why, these reflexion is very important to have. The life is full of things very nice and admirable who worth it to take time to appreciated it and not something we don't care. We have only one life who deserve our attention and this is very important thing to care about. Furthermore, with the time you will get more acknowledge of items surrondings as you will do quickly because at this stage, whole thing will to quick and you won't value it. You have to considered than sometimes this is no a choice in their life and perharps rather enjoyed this life is to live it intensely. This is something very respecteful as well. If you can take one example, people who have shorter life and want to live deeply, they haven't choice to do it if they want to find it out. These are our own choice.
