S People do not do exercise nowadays because their long working times. Due to inactive life they will lead to some healthy problems in the future. For young people some of foundation such as universities or their schools can help students to avoid inactive lifestyle. Initially, they can forced the sportive activity to students to get habit for them. First of all, educational foundations can showed many paths to students to be healthy. Universities can help children to be active with antrenors, dieticians and teachers who are professional in field of sports. Nevertheless, students will teach to manage their time thanks to activity life. If universities forced to do sports activities at least three times per week, students' psyhological lives will be more regular for them because it is the fact that exercise help people who have a depression or anything psyhological disease. On the other hand, students have not managed their time owing to heavy working. Universities want that students use their time efficiently. Furthermore, If students do exercise properly, they can motivated substantially when they do other hard working. This way which is applied by the schools is not forced in fact. It just provided for healthy life. Some people think that universities or schools can not forced students to do exercise. Their idea is wrong I think because Universities do not get money from students with this path. They think it terms of economical play that is played for money. Even they think it is a wrong, no doubt that exercise help students significiantly. To sum up, it is a well known the fact that exercises help all people for healthy life. Thereby, universities should forced students doing exercise three times per week. Thanks to this path studens get used to do sports in their life.
