S Hello my people. I would like to share to you the best tool that I have been used in the whole of my life to practicing writing in English. One day I was talking with my English teacher about the difficulties that I have when I'm trying to study English alone and the main problem that I have is the difficult to know if what I'm writing is correct or incorrect ? The teacher told me about a good tool to verify my essays online, he said, it was developed by Cambridge University experts and it is similar to the corrections that I do in your essays. In the begginning I did not believe that it was possible, but I accessed the site and after I did my first essay I understand that it is true and unbelieveble tool, the inteligency artificial is amazing and it can make good suggestions to you improve your english words. I really love the suggestions that IA does , sometimes I think that is difficult to understand where is the mistakes, because they don't provide details about what is wrong in my phrase, so you need to look at careffully to discover the problem. After sometime it can be easy to know how the inteligency artificial works and you use it to improve a lot your writings and change your vocabulary.
