S My reasons for learning English To make a long story short,l will place my reasons in two different paragraphs. First,l'm Chinese. which means l'm foregin. lf l can study the English launguge very well,l can get respect from my fellow sudents. Both in my own home China or in the America. l can have a life making by just being a professor in a college teaching business English. Second,almost 2/3 the people in the world speak English. So l can have lots of friends with just using one lauguge. The third reason however,was a little like the disadvantages of studying English. The only problem is,that l'm afraid of if my English was so well,we can't commuicate. So better just do some at a time. And here l'm not only talking about me,l'm talking to all of the guys and gals who study English. If you really want to study English,l recommend you to be a student teacher to see how you can teach.
