S Nowadays telling or not telling lie is not paid attention by actually teenagers who represent our future. If we take a look to the history there have always been people who tell lies. Even in children fairytales had villains who are liars. But in today's modern world population of people who can tell lies increased. The majoritiy of people tell lies esaily and without thinking if it is ethic to tell it. In my opinion in the future lies will be being told by people because there can be situations which's are dangerous and vital. For me in that kind of situations it is acceptable to tell lies whichs not affect other people's life. As I mentioned today especially teenagers made telling lies piece of life. I want to give example in my life. When I was I child I used to be naughty student in the class. One day I had an argument with my classment about football field usage. I had started telling bad words to my classmate before she did the same thing to me. After hours I came to my home, my mother asked me if I was guity in that argument and I lied to her. The day after my mother learned the truth and she felt very bad. On that day I understood we mustn't tell lies for little things. If I hadn't told that lie on that day I would have told lies nowadays. In conculution, we should be honest. Everyone need to understand the importance of honesty.
