S Hi,Pen Friend. I was thinking,and l thought l should recommed you some entertainment. So picked this film out for you. It's called,Fire Anger. This movie has blood,knife,and guns. The main story revolves around a police that catch the bad and deal with bloody consequences. I'm not going to give you anymore information or you won't have any interest of watching it. By the way,this is my favorite movie. I think you should watch it because it only used the movie 24-69 main characters,and they perfectly interpretated the absolute battle between the world's gray,black,and whites. of course,villans alwayes lose. But not in this movie. In this movie,the director let's us to take a tour at the world that the black is the abosolute ruler of the world. Like living in the holocaust all day. Anyway,be sure to watch that film! I will wait for your reply a week later. Best wishes, Gregory
