S Well, It is not a simple question, I don't like noise, and currently like sleep in a dark and quiet place, I don't need sleep more than ten hours daily, but need sleep eight hours every day. If i don't sleep at least eight hours, I have no energy in the next day. But it is not a rule to me, when I go camp, I frequently sleep less than eight hours, because I am in a different situation, In these cases, i usually sleep in a tent, and in this place there are less darkness and much noise.
