S Nowadays, some people has a bad habit of using the mobile phone, what is not true is the mobile phone is bad to human beings, many officers can use it to work online, and get information about what happen around us, waht's more, we can also invest in stocks, and students can use it to study online. So, personally speaking, I can't agree with this idea. First and foremost, the mobile phone is benefit to us, we can use it to contant with our parents, and paly games to unwind us, I know there are many debates about how the mobile phone should be banned, my opinion is absolutely not. As what I said, mobile phone is benefit to us, but try to transpositional consideration, you may discover that prople can't leave the mobile phone anymore, if the mobile phone was banned in the public areas, the individuals can't ring others, or get some information in time, and the time also becomes difficult to control. Additionally, mobile phone may do harm some people, they decrease the relationship between the family, and make people become estranged from each other. However, it is not the mobile phone's faults, but the way to use them, and I think the town council should lead people use it in a correct way, but not banned it in public areas, this method will sharpen contradictions, and make the situation worse, even destabilize society. All in all, as the saying goes, we should be channeling, not blocking, we should lead the citizens a right way to use them, and I believe the mobile phone, the crystallization of science and technology,can make the society more wonderful.
