S Well, This tool is very important to improve my skills in writting, the online feedback is the best practice to fix the flaws in the texts. Things that I liked: Online feedback, Short tasks, small problems to solve, progress analisys, levels to pass, and also being an online tool is very important too. Things that I didn't like: graphics that show the complete progress because I can see only the last ten ratings. One diferential of this tool is the intuitive design, It's very simply to use and confortable to write, other featured that can be improve our skills in writting text maybe it's an online dictionary, this feature would make writing much easier. Other caracteristics of this tool, is qas the easy that i have to find in an online search, I found this tool in a simple search on google, and the free option to exercise my writting is the factor that caught my attention. If was possible, I was recommend this tool to every student that need improve the skills in english language. I just in the beggining of learning, but yet see the importance of this.
