S We need music in our lives. Seroiusly,l can't belive why can you even call a life without BGM a life. Here's why l think so:First,we need to listen to songs without music and compare it to regular songs with the BGM. Totally big difference. When you are listening a song without BGM,you're not listening a song,you are listening to some random people particularly reading this song lyrics to you. Most importantly,music can help us relax. Like when you have a hard day,you can put on any music you like when you are in the shower to get your muscles slow down a take a break. If the stuff l said before did not persude you into believeing that music is impoartant,good. If yes,even better. Because just imagine what will the world be like without bands and CDs. The happy birthday song will just be some lyrics. The parties will be just a cool set up with refreshments and games. Not fun.
