S Music is playing an important part in our lives, I think. Having said that it is the same like a fish without the water. Let us break andlook at the importance of the music in our life. Imagine music as a very powerful tool that has a capability to change our mood positively or even negatively. To give an illustration, when you listen to music you do not love too much, it makes you feel angry. Conversely, you can listen to music that makes you feel happy. However,there is also a state of mind in which we need a pouse. That isto say, our mindis in a state where music can cause negative feelings and what we need is a silence. By and large music has a disruptive effect on our brain. Finally, I cannot imagine my life without music. Music helps me overcome difficulties, change my attitude, think better over something andII would continue. Last but not least, music keeps me above water in most things.
