S For me the music is not important. It is foundamental! I can not live without her! I listen to the music all day and all days. Music is culture. Every period of time, every historical event had his own soundtrack. Just think of Bob Dylan and the american revolution, or Also Guthrie and the vietnam war for example. Another, Pink Floyd and the Berlin wall. And every nation has his own kind of music! It is fantastic! Music is also entertainment, concert and disco are some examples. Another, music is relax too. And we can not forget music therapy. But music is also natural noises like wind, rain, the waves on the sea, animal sounds. Can we imagine a world without music? A film without soundtrack? I think the answer is no! Music is a kind of magic in our life.
