S Every professional would like getting a good job, with a great salary, enough equipment to work and with options to learn more to do his labor the best. This is a rasonable desire becuase each professional invested a lot time and money in his academic trainning. However, all these professionals forget the firts reason to train in a particular career, which is to solve problems, help and support actions to improve human lives. Particularly, this reason is remarkable in healthy careers as medicine and nursing, because they swore to help people. Unfortunatelly, selfishment is growing up and searching of good and comfortable life as better as posible is more important. Further, goverments don't encourage to medical doctors to contribuite with medical services to these people. Goverments don't want to offer to doctors good salaries or safe places for working. So, eventhough a few medical doctors want to help these people, they are not able to do it because they don't have access to basics supplies and conditions to do their work.
