S The School of the future will be better than in the past, with the advent of the internet access to information is increasing impressivively. I think schools will be different in many aspects, the learning process will be enhanced with many digital technologies like virtual reality, artificial intelligence and digital plataforms. Althought these technologies are better current ones, I thing that some things might will not change, such as dependence on the professor, the contact with other childrens, the school environment that favors interaction and the different levels to reach knowledge gradually. Perhaps education is tailored to the particular needs of students, leading them to reach their greatest individual potential. The form of education itself impose the same form of education on all childrens, and this is not the best practice to train smart people, it just prepares the children to solve the same problems by getting them to into low-paying jobs. We need to change the format of the schools to improve the education of society so that we can compare ourseves with people from developed contries. The power is in our hands!
