S In my opinion, music is awesome. I listen to music to do almost everything in my life, like run, clean the house or work. In my case, music make me fell happy and strong to struggle with my life. I don't know how I will survive without a music. One of my favourite things to do is going out to pub and listen to the music and drink beer. I like almost all kind of music, but my favourite are rock, eletronic and mpb. In 2019 I went to Tomorrowland, it is one of the most famous eletronic festival that has in the world, it is located in Belgium and happens only in the weekend. In the Tomorrowland is possible to know people from every country in the world, all of them are looking for relax, enjoy the music and sometimes make a date. It was my first experience in the big festival and I can say that it was gourgeous , I feel the flow of the music and the energy of the place inside of my heart and my mind. I suggest to everybody that like music to go to place like this to know exactly how much do you like music and people, for me it was very good because I love music.
