S Dear Sam, I am writing this letter to you because I want to temind you our for tomorrow in the afternoon. First of all, I will be working until five o\u00B4clock in the afternoon, for that reason you can come to my house since six o\u00B4clock in the afternoon Secondly, you don\u00B4t have to bring nothing because yesterday, I bought our dinner, we are going to eat pizza, drink red wine and we will have a very nice dessert made of chocolat. Finally, if you don\u00B4t remember where is my house, you will only have to know where is the bus station in the main avenue, because my house is very near from there. When you get there, call me and I will go to pick you up. Regards from your friend Miguel
