S I think that using computers and tablets in schools and universities has both advantages and disadvantages. Nowadays, the world become more modernize than the last years. Especially, the students use computers as a learning tool. One of the advantages of using computers is that the students don't need to carry heavy backpack anymore. They can go to school happily. The next one is that cause the students use computers and tablets in schools, they are familier with technology since they was young. So, they will not have any problems about technology in workpalce. But there are some disadvantages of using computers and tablets in schools. Some of the students have eye diseases because of using computers. And computers and tablets are expensive nowadays, so some students can't effort to buy it. In conclusion, although there has some disadvantages in that statement, I still believe that using computers and tablets in schools and universities is essential thing for students.
