S As you know arrangement of your office at the workplace you work in is playing an important role. Moreover, it also has an impact on your fillings, comunication with your coworkers and as well affect others. Some workers prefer to be in closed and separated areas equiped with no special furniture. However, they put a lot of effort to arrange their offices in a simple way but in the spirit of the latest design and modern furniture to feel much more comfortable. To be more precise, they prefer their offices lighted by the natural light from the outside through the windows. From the above, we can undrstand that those people have a weakness for presenting a well-being. They also like small and well-organized places where all things have its own place. In addition, they must visually present their success in the way to show their awards and diplomas on the walls of their offices. The other group of workers prefers simply arranged offices with no special design. Those offices usually have purposeful arrangement. By and large, simple arranged office dominates. Notably, places for other coworkers who can come in to discuss a problem or even organize a meeting is not missing. Conversely, those places in which workers spend at least eight hours per day would be comfortable. For example, their workplaces are equiped with places where people can meet and have a short break for discussion. In my view, the second example of an arrenged office seems to be the most persuasive. To clarify my opinion, I am a person who love to be surrounded by positive and communicative people sharing their ideas. If someone ask me of what I will suggest to have in my office, I would say nothing special \u2013 in a roundabout kind of way. Last but not least, the more effort you put into the design of your office the comfortable you will feel there.
