S Hi Sam, I'd like to tell you a tomorrow's plan. At first, please come here at 7 pm. I will be able to prepare for your dinner until then. When you come here, would you like to bring some drink such as a alcohol and soft drink. In addition, it's the first time to come our house. Accordingly, I want to let you know how to get here. When you arrive at Tokushima Station, you exchange from train to bus. You can find No.2 bus stop, then you ride on it bound for Hokke river. Please drop off at Kawaminami bus stop. If you call me, I will welcome you to the bus stop. I'm looking forward to seeing you and have a good time with you. Thanks, John
