S It is more important to be healthy than to be rich, this statement could be aplied for some preople but is not a rule for everyone. Sometimes be healthy is not guarantee for a happy life, be healthy without enought money to supply the basic needs is not a desirable life. In the other hand, be rich without health is not enjoyable, the most important thing is the balance between the both things. People need enought money to survive with the minimum confort and be healthier enought to live without restrictions. Some people work hard to save money during the entire life and spent these money trying solve health problems that had created trying save more money. Be healthy or be reach is a delicated topic, some people prefer one and some people prefer other, we need be understand what is more important to us and don't make value judgment about the other's decision. If a person is happy beeing healthy without money or beeing happy with lots of money without health, no problem, this is a particular choose.
