S Taveling is one thing that made people fell better in their lives, not only to share experiences with friends but to improve their own life experience, When we know a new culture and visit new places our universe expands and we know that our daily work make sense. In my opinion, the future of travel will not be much different that actual, maybe some things will be different like the transport or things like that, but the traver per si or the desire for traveling will not change. The need for travelling might still be the same, people need travel, it is an habit raised in all humans, and this will not change. One thing I think will be different in the future, is the places that people will go, some places in the earth will be changed by the global warming, and some people will choose other places to avoid problems with climate. Another thing I think will be different, is the improvement of digital solution to travelers, like automatic translators that will enable every person to communicate with others without the language barrier.
