S Exercise is important for our health, but are there things that are more important? I think not. Without health we can't do nothing, we depend of our body to do everything in our lives. If we don't care our own health, who would do it for us? Exercise is not a enjoyable ting to do, but is necessary, we need exercive thirty minutes daily to be healthier, it is not necessary more than this time to make our body better than persons who don't exercise. Sedentarism is a moder problem wich causes a lot of problems in society, many health problems might be solved exercesing in daily routine. Some people argue that have no time to exercise, but it is not true, if you analyse the rountine of these people, you will find time to practice some exercises, exercise is not a question of time, is a matter of wanting to. If you want, you will find time do exercese, money is important, but without health you won't be able to use the maney you save. Think about that, and change your life style.
