S In this year, I wish learning English in an advanced level, I will be pleased if in the end of the year I have been developed the skill necessary to talk with others without mistakes. Today I am in B2 level of TOEFL, I wish I have achieved the level C1 of TOEFL to work easily with foreign people. The areas of learning I want to improve is related to conversation or writting, I need achieve a level that will able me work without restrictions and that make me more confident to negociate in a high level with Americans than currently I am able to. To achieve these goals, I am studying four hours a day, every day a week, I bought some books to improve my English level through self study, and I have a particular teacher to help me achieve the goals I set to me. I am particularly interested in learn English as fast as I can, I get a job that involves speak English, the work start in December, because that, I have about fifteen days to achieve the C1 Level of TOEFL. This is a good chalenge to me.
