S Video games are very popular with children. However, some parents feel that video games can have a negative impact on their children, but others believe that they may have some positive effects. As other things in the life, playing videogames has not positive or negative impact if this would be used with moderation, lets share some examples: If you drink much you will have negative impact in your life, if you don't drink you will have negative impact too because you won't have social interaction. In one hand if you watch news every day, you will be crazy, in the other hand if you don't see any news, you will get desinformed. As you see, when we talk about extremes behaviors, we are talking about problems and negative impacts in our life. The secret is not about playing video games and it positive or negative impact, the secret is balance the use to have just benefits without issues. Some parents argue that video games increase the violent acts from children, but it is not proved, some children have psicological problems that is not originated in the video games, this children need be treated as isolated cases and not as normal cases applied for everyone. Is proved that video games improve the brain activity and prevent some diseases such Ausimer and other neurologiacal problems in oldery. Video games is an intertainment tool, and need be used as it. The only problem that can be caused by video games, it the isolation that occur when youngers use it for long hours a day, they became anti-social, and this is a real problem to be avoided by parents. How I said earlier, video games are not problems as long as they are used sparingly.
