S When a student decide to study in a foreign country many skills are improved, and many advantages have taken such improvement in a foreign language, the experience in other culture, another people that the student met, and other advantages like relationship hability. The only disadvantage taked at studying in another coutry is the distance from home that makes the student feel apart from their families, and probably had lost many local events. I wish everybody could study in a foreign country, but it is not a reality for the most people, in Brazil for example, only one percent of the population have acess to a foreign university, in rare cases a poor person is able to travel to another coutry to study. I had a particular experience studying in another country, I take my master degree in a French university, and that was a momorable experience, I loved got contact with other culture and differnt behaviors, when I taveled to France I don't have enough hability to talk in English but that travel forced myself to study more and as result I am better in conversation and I am able to get positions in international companies. If you have possibility to study in a foreign country, don't think much, just accept and go ahead, you will like the experience and will remember that experience forever. If you don't have enough money to pay for a particular university, try do language courses, they are more cheap than degrees and you will experience another culture in the same way, with the same advantages.
