S Dear Sam, I hope this email finds you well. As we both know, tomorrow we finally meet. It's been ages since I've seen you last time! I'm very glad that you found some time to share with me and we can have a little fun. Please, be at my place at 6:00 PM. I thought we could play board games, so if you have a favourite one you can bring it with you. Also, if you could take some snacks with you, that would be grate. I'm planning to prepare a hot meal (my specialty) and coctails. My house is at the corner of Franciszkanska and Mlynarska streets. It's next to the big clothing store, so I'm sure you will find it easily. In case of any troubles, do not hesitate to just call me. I hope to see you soon. Love, D.
