S Sam, I\u00B4m looking forward to receive you in my house tomorrow. I was thinking of all of the fun things that we could do. I thought that we could play different board games or video game or even maybe them both. We should also go outside and play soccer and basketball with my neighbours. You can come right after the lunch so that we can enjoy every minute. You don\u00B4t need to bring much, just your clothes and the toothbrush. That\u00B4s all. I\u00B4m not sure how well you know my location, so here are some tips of how to get here. I pretty sure that you are familiar with the John\u00B4s market. So, you will have to turn right after it and then you\u00B4ll gonna count three traffic lights and then you\u00B4ll gonna turn left, left and right. My house it\u00B4s at the closed condominium called Bright Garden. When you get here, just text me and I will receive you at the front. If you have any doubts, just called me and I will try to help you.
