S How music is important in our lives? I think music is very important in our lives. Do you know when we are a kid, we were listened the llulaby to fall a sleep. When we are from 3 to 5 years old, we learn music from school. When we are teens we listen music every day. Pop, rock, edm, classical,.... many type of music for every one. Music is a diffirent way to tell a story. Anthem music is a story about a country. Love music is a story about love. It doesn't matter when the music is appear, the story still have this meaning. Some music make us feel enthusiasm, some music make us feel bad, some make us relax. Do you ever imagine what were the world be like without music? I can't imagine that. The life will very bored.
