S Music have been the Art with more changes and evolution during the last 30 years, currently in the siciety there are many differents style of music and for that reason the most interesting question has arisen in the music industry "Do we need music in our life? I think that at moment music as important as eat because there exist many dificult moments where music can feel us specials and comfortable. My point of view is that music help people to comunicate their feelings and feel better with themself, I can not imagine my life and a society without music, it will be so different and sad. Actually many studies say that music help the health because music can be decrease stres and ansiety, even music is like a tratamient for people that suffer depresion and live with a constantly sadness. For me music it's the best way to say love things and transmit feelings to other. However, people think that not all music is good but I don't agree because not matter if music is created with a piano or a drums, it will be a perefect melody.
