S Sometimes there are people who ask themselves if music is important in our lives, and without any doubt the answer is yes. Music is present in the most of events in our lives, for example when we are celebrating a wedding, the most important situation is the dance between the couple. When we are celebrating, a bad song could make stop the party or a good song could increase the fun. In general, life without music would be very bored, when I am with friends I usually say "if the music didn't exist, I would have to invent it," and this is true. in my personal case, I listen to music every day, when I train, I listen music, when I drive, I listen music. I listen music all the time. Whitout music, our lives would be less interest, we would not see films with expectation, the qeues in the supermarket would be worse. My point of view can't be discussed because we have many online platforms to bring the music with us anywhere and anytime
