S Nowadays, it is often said telling the truth is always important, but it has ever been telling lies an option. In the following lines I will deeply discuss about this concerning issue. On the one hand, telling the truth, you will never be worried about what you have said. Therefore, it is highly possible you would be more confident, if you had not told any lies in your life. But seldom do we find people of that kind. However, you could be in troubles as long as you tell the truth. Unfoutunatly, It is being widely known how dangerous a situation could be when you tell to the wrong person what he is not willing to hear. On the other hand, lying may save you in some context from worst consequences. Despite it is impossible to lie the rest of your life, lying would be utterly useful in certain situations such us when you were a child and you had not do your homework. However, and fourtunately in my opinion, people generaly get cought when they say a lie. But, sadly, telling lies, you cannot only hurt yourself but others people feelings. To sum up, I vividly believe lying should never be acceptable as far as it can cause a negative impact in someones lifes. As far as I am concerned, we must be the only responsables of our actions and so on of our lies.
