S Dear Sam, I'm writing you this mail about the music concert that I went to. First of all, it was so amazing! Ed Sheraan has performed there for awhile and then came my favorite one Shawn Mendes, he performed for a whole hour! For me that was the happiest hour of the entire day! Then there was a band that I didn't know but their music is so optimistic and full of life, I really love it. Secondly, even though the concert was very crowded yet it was so safe, there was security members every where and they made sure there's a safe environment for us all. They checked our bags carefully at the entrance and they took every toothy thing and they also took fireworks from people there because as you know it caused a lot of harm last concert, so they made sure everything is safe inside. I really hoped you were there with me, you would have enjoyed a lot! But it's fine we will go together to the next one so make sure you put that in your schedule from now. Have a nice day Sam! Yours, Sophia
