S Nowadays, as long as we fourtunately have more free time, one issue has become really important to consider, namely: how we want to live our lifes? On the one hand, living such a calm and relaxing life, you will probably live until 100 years. However, despite living a large life could have its pros, I sinceraly believe it will tragically end up by being not only bored but also in some way severe and ruthless. For example, living more than your reslatives, you will probably see how they die what could be such a harsh punishment. On the other hand, having such a large life, it is not required in order to have a pleintful life. As far as I am concerned, living an intense live, you will wisely appreciate every single second of your existence. What is more, you will be sufficiently free to do whatever you want with your life as long as you know you will die. Only when we understand our temporary existence, we will be able to move forward and live our dreams. In brief, unless you want to have a bored existence, I wiill highly recommend you to be as active as possible in your daily life. We do not know how much time are we going to live, only time will tell. Hence, a lot has to changed in ourselves in order to live the way we dream and we want. To sum up, I totally believe an intense life it is a good deal better than a long and bored life.,
