S What is my favourite season of the year? This is a very good issue and answering it is not simple. However, I think my favourite season is autumn. I love autumn because it is a season of changing. I can see the changing all around me. The temperature is warm and the sun is not so hot. The climate is wet because of rains. Autumn is the season in which it is raining the most rather than the others. The days are short and the sun goes down early. I can see the changing on the trees. Their leaves turn their color from green to different shades of red like orange, yellow and brown. And the leaves on the trees are less, they fall down and cover streets, gardens or paths. The mountains are whole colored. And what about your favourite seoson?
