S I have recently discovered Write and Improve, a new writing tool for learners of English that is easy to use and helps to write better. The main tool's features are many tasks that you can use to write texts and submit it for correction, the application identify what is wrong and make recommendations to improve your writting. This tool is helpful because you can see recommendations in real time, it show you a grid with IELTS scale and the position of your text between the levels A1 to C2. IT show you the words that are wrong and the tasks have different levels, you can start at the Beginner level, advance to intermediate and advanced level. There are tasks to improve your business writing and new tasks are added montly. One thing I like about the tool is the option to write the task I want, I don't have to do all the intermediary tasks to go to the advanced lever for example. I have some difficulties and miss some features as tips to use in my texts such as the right use of collocations, how can I improve my sentences and features to help me create better phrases. Some recommendation for improve the tool include: More awards to make the writer engaged, tips to help in the writting, a graphic with filters to show our entire evolution throught the levels and a personalized plan of study. Maybe, we can have a guide to compare our writing evolution to some guide ruller, are we in the correct path or not?
