S Dear Alex. I'm very glad to have your invitation to the party this afternoon. It sound very nice and interesting but I'm sorry to refuse it. Because this afternoon, I need to go to my graduate party. It's really meaningfull to me. I will have the best moment with my family and my boy friend. I'm sorry that I have to rufuse the days to meet you again. It's very pleasent of you to think about that for me. How about next Saturday afternoon? I don't have any plan on that day. We will go to the biggest cinema in Ha Noi and choose your favourite movie. " Magic train ," isn't it? Then we will go around Ho Guom Lake. I heard that there were a lot of games and street foods. And we will have the best memory together. See you on that day! Your best friend Tee
