S From, Sam Hi, Alex, l' m so sorry that l can' t go to your party, l will give you a gift as an apology. Sorry! Oh, and speaking of absent, let me tell you why l was not at the party and you will know it all. lt begins at a restarunt. Me and my family were at a KFC fastfood place. We had already placed our order and was finding a place to sit. The bottom floor were full, so we headed up to the upper floor to sit. But just as we headed up, l slipped on a not entirely drunk bottle of juice. That' s it. The next minute l had found myself lying on the floor. Moaning and felt awful. When we' re at the hospital, we found out that my leg is broken due to an uncontrolled free fall of the stairs. l had to do mutiple surgeries to ensure that my leg bone healed entirely. The whole cost took a big bite of mom and dad' s bank acount. But luckily, we our financial problem was solved by the money we get for sueing the fastfood place.
