S Almer\u00EDa, I live in Almer\u00EDa, a place where you have a huge range of things to do. You can go shopping to the mall called "Torrec\u00E1rdenas" or to the boulevard where you will find amazing things. If you wanted to do cultural activities you would have to go to the "alcazaba" or the Pakita museum, where you'd find many exhibitions. However, if you are a nocturnal mammal you will enjoy of the many clubs and restaurants that we also have in the boulevard, although they are more expensive than the bars that we can find in others streets. Finally if you have doubsts or you want further details, please contact with us in the tourism office, we are in the main street, find us it's a piece of cake.
