S Alex, I want to ask apologise because I am not going to a party this Satursay. I will be busy with my studies for the TOEFL test on Monday. This test is much important for me, I need then to try study at the international university. As much as aplications for university it becames I need to be able to pass to test. So, study is everything I need. I hope you understand. We could meet in another Saturday, when I will be free. You can come at my house and sleep here. I make a couple of things for us to eat like chips and brownie. We can invite other friends to join us. So, we would play deck and board and also watch some horror movies. It will be a very fun meet if you accept. I hope you'll forgive me and understand why I'm not coming to your party.
