S Nowadays, because of the internet and the globalization, we have more hobbies and new ways to spend our spare time than previously. I think that I have a lot hobbies, my mother used to say that I spend more time playing than working. I like playing videogames with my laptop, doing exercise alone in my own gym and hanging out with my girlfriend doing new activities. If I could add a hobby, It would be ciclying but it will have to be in the future, because it is not my cup of tea. I only can do these activities on weekdays and in the afternoons when I finish my duties, because in the mornings I must work in my base and later do the housework and homework. If Finally, I have to say that I have a good balance between my duties and hobbies and I'm very happy and grateful with my daily routine.
