S Nowadays we have many resources on the Internet to practice our English skills, in my personal opinion the hardest part to practice is writing, where you have to be very carefully and imaginative and where each fail can cost a lot. One of the best tools that the students have to practice this skill is a website called "Write and Improve," where I have been doing a lot of exercises. It is a website where you can practice a lot, and receive good inputs. You can start from a very low level, to break the ice, until a very hard level, where you would have to be an expert in this subject. It is said that the good things are expensive, but in this case, another advantage could be that this website is totally free, you will only have to register in the website and enjoy learning. On the other hand, this website has some disadvantages in its use, for instance the corrections are made by a machine, and it could not be perfect, leaving some fails without correction, or giving wrong feedbacks. The fact is that a native teacher is much better to learn a language, but not all of us can afford a teacher, for that reason even with those posibilities I continue recommend you this website. Finally, I strongly believe that th advantages are much better than the disadvantages and if you use this website, you will find many useful resources.
