S Hi Alex! I'm so sorry for that I can't go to your party this Saturday . What a pity! I'll have to pick up my old friend , Tom at the airport that day. I told you about this guy who used to be my neighbor when I was a kid. We went to the same primary school, middle school and high school together at that time. But when we planed to go to the same university , his family suddenly emigrated to the United States. Time past quickly, we haven't seen each other for six years since he went to America. So I can't cancel this plan, I must give him a big and warm hug at the airport when I meet him. That would be an excited moment for two old friends for a long time no see. If you could change your party time to this Sunday , I could take Tom to your party , that must be very happy party for us.
