S Dear Billal, I have been in a lot of trips during my life, but the last one was the best trip that I have taken in my life. I traveled to London last week and it's such a great city that I will never forget it. I saw many great things like the Westminster Abbey, a river called Thames, the London Tower, the london bridge and other great ancient places. We went to the national museum, we saw the change of the guard at the royal palace and so many activities that I can't remember right now. we also ate the tipical dish, fish and fries, but it wasn't my cup of tea. I'm pretty sure that if I had the opportunity, I would come back to London, because I fell in love of London. Drop me a line,
