S Hi Alex, I am very happy to listen to you. How are you? I hope so. Today, I am going to writing to you about your party next Saturday. Unfortunatly, I can not come: I am very sorry, and I want to apologise to you. I would have been happy to see to you and the others friends. Saturday I have an important job interview in London. A big society is looking for young chemical engineer like me. It is a huge opportunity to me, than I must go! I am going to stay in London all week but, on my return, if you want, we could meet. Maybe, in an italian restorant! And than, with the opportunity, you could tell me about your party. Also, I will tell you about my job interview. What do you think? Let me know as soon as possible and, have a good party! Bye Andrea
