S My home town is very beautifull. I love this place because I grew up here and I learnt so many things from this place. There are many parks, restaurants and library. The park is febulous and you will get all the things that is required for you. There are many restaurants, swing, beatifull flowers and trees inside the park. There are many shopping malls you can buy as per your requirment and all are in afordable prices so no need to worry about prices and all. The cinema halls are also fantastic there. You will get 5-6 cinema halls upper to lower class. If you want to spent lot then you will get that type of cinema halls as well. The hotels are fabulous. You like the hotels because they are fully furnished and all things are availabe inside the hotel no need to worry about restaurant, swimming pool, parking place and swing. The hotels are afordable and you can book online or offline. There are many bar and pubs if you want to enjoy your night they you can go to that places so you just have to tell the driver that you want to go to bar and he will drop to you that place and the places are safe and secure no need to worry about anything. There are helpline number for that if you feel any difficulty you can call to that number and you will get help.
